<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cross-v">cross <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /krɒs/    美 /krɔːs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 交叉；(与) 交叉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The roads cross just outside the town.
这些道路正好在城外交叉。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She sat down and <strong>crossed her legs</strong>.
她坐下来，跷起了二郎腿。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>越过；横过；渡过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cross a river / bridge/ desert
渡河/过桥/穿越沙漠</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t cross. The light is red.
别过去，现在是红灯。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="cross-out-off">cross out / off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>划掉；删除 (错字等)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You’ve spelt it wrong. Cross it out and try again.
你拼错了。划掉再写一遍。</p></div></div>